;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":party_popper:"&gt;🎉&lt;/span&gt;We invite everyone to submit their abstracts for consideration. Share your insights, discoveries, and innovations in Utilities.&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":link:"&gt;🔗&lt;/span&gt;Submit your abstract here:&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;A class="" href="https://lnkd.in/emysya8k" target="_self" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://lnkd.in/emysya8k&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
